Name:                securemem
Version:             0.1.0
x-revision: 1
Synopsis:            abstraction to an auto scrubbing and const time eq, memory chunk.
Description:
    SecureMem is similar to ByteString, except that it provides a memory chunk that
    will be auto-scrubbed after it run out of scope.
